Grand Theft Auto V is an open world, action-adventure video game developed by Rockstar North and published by Rockstar Games. It was released on 17 September 2013 for the PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 consoles. It is the fifteenth title in the Grand Theft Auto series, and the first main entry since Grand Theft Auto IV was released in 2008. As one of the last titles to release exclusively during the seventh generation of video game consoles, Grand Theft Auto V was highly anticipated preceding its release.

Grand Theft Auto V is played in third-person and combines driving and action gameplay in an open world environment, allowing the player to interact with the game world at their leisure. The game is set within the fictional state of San Andreas, which is based on Southern California, affording the player free roam over the world's countryside and the fictional city of Los Santos, which is based on Los Angeles. The single-player story is told through three player-controlled protagonists whom the player switches between—Michael, Trevor and Franklin—and the story follows their efforts to plan and execute six large heists to accrue wealth for themselves. An online multiplayer mode is included, allowing up to sixteen players to engage in both co-operative and competitive gameplay in a recreation of the single-player setting.

iG7UdnQfdB8.title: [HD] 산속의 KTX-산천 / 山中のKTX-山川 / KTX-Sancheon in the mountains
iG7UdnQfdB8.description:
2012년 6월 1일, 강릉역에서 원주-강릉간 복선전철 기공식이 있었습니다.

그 때에 배경으로서 KTX-산천 24편성이 동원되었었으며, 6월 3일 다시 서울로 돌아왔습니다. 견인은 KTX 구원전용 기관차인 7574호가 담당하였습니다.

본 영상은 6월 3일, 서울로 돌아가기 위해 KTX-산천이 스위치백을 지나, 영동선 심포리역과 통리역을 통과하는 모습입니다. 이 모습을 촬영하기 위해 전국에서 많은 철도동호인들이 이 열차가 운행하는 영동선, 태백선, 충북선 주변에 집결, 촬영하였었습니다.

2012年6月1日韓国の江原道の江陵駅で原州-江陵間複線電鉄の鍬入れ式(起工式)がありました。
大統領や長官も列席する大した式だったんですので、その背景でKTX-山川が動員されました。ソウルから江陵まで往復の甲種回送はKTX救援専用の機関車7574号が担当しますし、KTX-山川は6月3日ソウルへ帰りました。

この動画はKTX-山川が嶺東線の深浦里駅と桶里駅を通過する風景です。
この風景を撮るために全国でたくさんの鉄ファンたちがこのスイッチバックの周りに集結しました。

1st June 2012, groundbreaking ceremony at Gangneung Station for new electric-double track railroad between Wonju and Gangneung.
KTX-Sancheon was returned to Seoul on 3rd June, running in the mountains leaded by Diesel Locomotive.

JmPWe4uquN4.title: How To Make Steel Targets:  Cheap & Easy!
JmPWe4uquN4.description:
How to easily and cheaply make DIY Steel Targets that hang and swing.  These homemade steel targets are made out of scrap steel plates (from scrapyard) or purchased hardened steel target plates, along with some common Shepherd's Hook's for outdoor gardening.  With a fresh coat of spray paint or a new adhesive paper target applied between uses, they are like new every time!  See below for more on this project and quick links to all materials needed!

**BEST Spinning Steel Targets with Auto Reset!:  http://amzn.to/2Etj43o

**AR500 10-in Steel Gong Target for all Calibers!:  http://amzn.to/2E0V0Hw

**Shepherds Hook's for Hanging Targets:  http://amzn.to/2GAVm68

**100-pack Adhesive Reactive 8-in. Splatter Targets:  http://amzn.to/2E44d1y

These homemade steel targets are a decent alternative to purchasing hanging steel or spinning targets, but nearly every variation of swinging or spinning steel target is available online for reasonable prices.  I use a readily available Shepherd's Hook to hang the steel plates.  Local salvage or recycling yards are the best place to get the steel and they usually are happy to sell it to you by the pound.  If you are nice they will even punch a hole in it for you with a propane torch.  You can also purchase Hardened Steel Target Plates (like AR500) with pre-cut holes for hanging in any (safe) fashion you wish.

If you want to take the steel targets a step further, it is nice to have some self-adhesive reactive paper targets on-hand to attach.  You can stick them to the face of the steel target for easy shot identification.


**Swinging Metal Target Systems:  http://amzn.to/2Etj43o
**AR500 Hardened Steel Hanging Targets:  http://amzn.to/2E0V0Hw
**Shepherds Hook's for Hanging Targets:  http://amzn.to/2GAVm68
